Copyright.RotationInfo: Based on the field notes in EDI files, all channels were collected in geographic coordinates; but the header of the INFO section says that original coordinates are all geomagnetic. ROTSPEC suggests geomagnetic. We have to assume that everything was rotated to geomagnetic, as per the ROTSPEC, before writing to file. Under that assumption, we are now rotating to geographic for archiving.
Copyright.AdditionalInfo: These data were converted from the original EDI SPECTRA format using EMTF FCU 4.0 developed by Anna Kelbert, USGS last updated in Nov 2017. This novel algorithm allows for estimation of full error covariances from cross-power spectra. We thank Xavier Garcia and Gary Egbert for valuable advice that helped develop the spectra conversion algorithm.
